{"tid":2198002,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港人堅持捍衞自由權利 獲美國「自由之家」頒發年度獎項","createTime":"2020-09-11T04:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T08:32:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b204a0ac65ec79737c0950c73173743aefb245b2","tid":2198002,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"香港人持續捍衞應有的權利與自由，再次獲得國際民權機構的肯定。美國著名支持民主發展的非政府組織「自由之家」(Freedom House)頒發年度獎項，有三個單位得獎，包括「香港民主運動」（Hong Kong&rsquo;s Pro-Democracy Movement），該組織讚揚港人堅持致力於「以新穎有創意的方法守衞下一代的權利」。香港民間人權陣線召集人岑子杰及前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒表示，獲獎是顯示港人追求的價值觀獲全世界認同、努力獲得肯定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200911/JSAFXDSXPJFFBMW2XKJCVORF2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200911%2FJSAFXDSXPJFFBMW2XKJCVORF2A%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=4e2bb32a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200911%2FJSAFXDSXPJFFBMW2XKJCVORF2A%2F&h=7a0a72b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200911/JSAFXDSXPJFFBMW2XKJCVORF2A/</a>"},{"pid":"43249d153fcdd7cf46de1d8bb2cc0590c5f183cf","tid":2198002,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df81793c634cc84f4f16fc7b0fdb17b84e421be","tid":2198002,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:58:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6cf30d0adf1ddf527aa57c37b0a9f9740d051778","tid":2198002,"uid":322642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:00:27.000Z","msg":"Thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2c76e83c3348489a3058beb993148cf4bac58d","tid":21980